  <title>Sort View</title>

  <p>To sort the current view:</p>
  <steps>
    <item><p>Select <guiseq><gui style="menu">View</gui><gui style="menuitem">Sort By...</gui></guiseq>.</p></item>
    <item><p>Select the column you want to sort, set if ascending or descending, then click <gui style="button">Sort</gui>.</p></item>
